Active@ Partition Recovery Enterprise Toolkit v5.3.717.

Have you ever faced situations such as Inadvertently deleted partitions (using fdisk or other programs) Damaged / Corrupted Hard Disk Logical Structure (for example due to boot virus)In such situations, one usually loses hope in recovering data and/or partition information, but until now.is a data recovery software tool that helps to recover deleted partitions and logical disks on hard drives. Can backup MBR (Master Boot Record), partition table, boot sectors. Restores MBR from backup if the partition structure was damaged by a virus or inadvertently deleted and you can also access any hard disk drive sectors using &quot;Disk Viewer&quot;. Creates disk image. Runs from PC startup disk.


Active@ Partition Recovery Enterprise Toolkit is an ultimate data recovery tool set. In addition to DOS and Windows versions of the software, it contains downloadable Bootable Windows ISO Image that you can burn to CD-ROM and boot Windows from this CD-ROM to recover partitions (including the system ones) as well as to recover particular files and folders from the familiar Windows environment. Active@ File Recovery utility is also included to allow you to save your files and folders in case of unsuccessful partition recovery (for example, the file system itself is severely damaged and Windows is unable to recognize the partition after recovery).


